spec_data.Name: dialog-devel
spec_data.Description:
Dialog is a utility that allows you to show dialog boxes (containing
questions or messages) in TTY (text mode) interfaces. This package
contains the files needed for developing applications, which use the
dialog library.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Mon 07 Aug 2017 04:23:55 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Development files for building applications with the dialog library
